title: Complete coverage: Parkland, Liberty advance to EPC girls volleyball final
text:
By Kyle Craig | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 23, 2015 1:55 AM, updated October 23, 2015 4:32 AM View/Post Comments 
Parkland and Liberty , the No. 1 and 2 teams according to lehighvalleylive's rankings, will meet in the Eastern Pennsylvania Conference final after semifinal victories on Thursday. 
The Trojans defeated Central Catholic and the Hurricanes topped Nazareth to book their spots in the conference final. 
Follow the links below for complete coverage and photos from the two semifinal matches: 
LIBERTY VS. NAZARETH
